# v0.58 — Health Persistence Across Chapters

### Changes
- GameState: added `saved_health` + `saved_max_health` fields (version bumped to 1.1)
- `_setup_level()`: applies saved health to player at chapter start
- `_update_label()`: auto-saves HP so Continue works correctly
- Between-chapter heal: +25 HP on chapter complete
- Title screen version: updated to v0.57 (released)

### Design Rationale
- Save system already existed; this makes it *work* for the gameplay loop
- Continue button now restores player to actual saved HP, not full heal
- Inter-chapter heal keeps tension without punishing too hard
- Backwards compatible: old save files without saved_health default to 100

